Fp%3E%3Cp%3EForeign%20election%20interference%20has%20increasingly%20been%20in%20the%20spotlight%20in%20the%20US%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fevidence-russia-meddled-in-us-election-2017-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERussian%20hacking%20controversy%20in%20the%202016%20election.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20long%20said%20that%20it%20does%20not%20interfere%20in%20the%20internal%20politics%20of%20other%20countries%2C%20a%20talking%20point%20Beijing%20often%20uses%20as%20a%20jab%20against%20US%20foreign%20and%20military%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20does%20not%20interfere%20in%20US%20elections.%20We%20oppose%20making%20China%20an%20issue%20based%20on%20election%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chinese%20Foreign%20Ministry%20told%20CNN%20when%20asked%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mfa.gov.cn%2Feng%2Fxwfw_665399%2Fs2510_665401%2F202401%2Ft20240131_11237282.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DWang%2520Wenbin%253A%2520The%2520presidential%2520election%2Cin%2520the%2520US%2527s%2520presidential%2520election.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EForeign%20Ministry%20spokesperson%20Wang%20Wenbin%20told%20reporters%20on%20Wednesday%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20presidential%20election%20is%20the%20domestic%20affair%20of%20the%20United%20States.%20China%2C%20committed%20to%20the%20principle%20of%20non-interference%20in%20others'%20internal%20affairs%2C%20will%20not%20interfere%20in%20America's%20presidential%20election.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-meddled-midterm-elections-biden-wouldnt-retaliate-us-intelligence-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20intelligence%20report%20declassified%20in%20December%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20China%20had%20been%20using%20%26quot%3Binfluence%20actors%26quot%3B%20to%20affect%20the%20outcomes%20of%20the%202022%20midterm%20elections%2C%20hoping%20to%20boost%20candidates%20seen%20as%20more%20pro-China.%20Iran%2C%20Russia%2C%20and%20Cuba%20also%20tried%20to%20interfere%20in%20the%20midterms%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20China's%20Foreign%20Ministry%20called%20the%20accusations%20%26quot%3Bgroundless%20and%20fabricated%20out%20of%20thin%20air.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-wont-meddle-presidential-election-xi-jinping-joe-biden-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706779167000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bb5fd87a3d271488767204%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-wont-meddle-presidential-election-xi-jinping-joe-biden-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China%20says%20it%20doesn't%20interfere%20in%20the%20politics%20of%20other%20countries%2C%20but%20US%20intelligence%20recently%20found%20that%20Beijing%20sought%20to%20influence%20the%202022%20midterms.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mloh%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Loh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-wont-meddle-presidential-election-xi-jinping-joe-biden-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'No%20farmers%2C%20no%20food'%3A%20Fires%20erupt%20during%20protests%20outside%20European%20Parliament%20in%20Brussels%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706779140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-european-parliament_6440099.jpg%3F20240201092110%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ffires-erupt-as-farmers-protest-outside-european-parliament-in-brussels-13061212%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Angry%20farmers%20have%20started%20fires%20outside%20the%20European%20Parliament%20building%20in%20Brussels%20in%20protest%20agai