o%20hiked%20the%20tax%20deducted%20at%20source%20(TDS)%20limit%20from%20Rs%2010%2C000%20to%20Rs%2040%2C000%20for%20post%20office%20savings%20and%20bank%20deposits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20the%20year%20the%20BJP%20defeated%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20government%2C%20the%20then%20Finance%20Minister%20P%20Chidambaram%20in%20his%20interim%20Budget%20had%20not%20made%20any%20significant%20changes%20in%20tax%20laws%2C%20but%20tweaked%20indirect%20taxes%20for%20a%20small%20set%20of%20sectors.%20He%20reduced%20excise%20duty%20from%2012%20per%20cent%20to%2010%20per%20cent%20on%20some%20goods%2C%20and%20gave%20relief%20to%20the%20automobile%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20there%20was%20no%20expectation%20of%20a%20change%20in%20tax%20slabs%20in%20this%20interim%20Budget%2C%20there%20was%20speculation%20about%20a%20possible%20increase%20in%20the%20standard%20deduction%20under%20the%20new%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20regime%20does%20not%20allow%20taxpayers%20to%20claim%20deductions%2C%20but%20eases%20the%20tax%20slabs%20for%20a%20wider%20range%20of%20incomes%2C%20while%20the%20old%20regime%20has%20a%20maximum%20tax%20slab%20of%2030%20per%20cent%20from%20a%20lower%20threshold%2C%20but%20also%20allows%20claims%20to%20be%20filed%20for%20deductions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20no%20hike%20in%20standard%20deduction%20under%20the%20new%20regime%2C%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20has%20not%20made%20any%20significant%20changes%20in%20taxation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706776020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2F6kah06f8_income-tax-_625x300_06_January_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Funion-budget-2024-tax-slab-trends-in-interim-budgets-why-they-dont-change-4972703%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20interim%20Budget%20this%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20year%20did%20not%20make%20any%20changes%20in%20tax%20slabs%2C%20in%20keeping%20with%20convention.%20Finance%20Ministe