tton%20repeatedly%20asks%20Shou%20Zi%20Chew%20about%20his%20links%20to%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-us-canada-68163420%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Direct%20Tax%20Demand%20Up%20To%20Rs%2025%2C000%20To%20Be%20Withdrawn.%20See%20Key%20Details%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20will%20not%20pursue%20taxpayers%20to%20recover%20old%20and%20disputed%20direct%20taxes%20up%20to%20Rs%2025%2C000%20till%20the%20financial%20year%202009-10%2C%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20said%20in%20her%20interim%20Budget%202024%20speech%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDirect%20taxes%20demand%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%20from%20the%20financial%20years%202010-11%20to%202014-15%20will%20also%20be%20withdrawn%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20will%20benefit%20about%20one%20crore%20taxpayers%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20There%20are%20a%20large%20number%20of%20petty%2C%20non-verified%2C%20non-reconciled%20or%20disputed%20direct%20tax%20demands%2C%20many%20of%20them%20dating%20as%20far%20back%20as%201962%2C%20which%20continue%20to%20remain%20on%20the%20books%2C%20causing%20anxiety%20to%20honest%20taxpayers%20and%20hindering%20refunds%20of%20subsequent%20years.%20I%20propose%20to%20withdraw%20such%20outstanding%20direct%20tax%20demands%20up%20Rs%2025%2C000%20pertaining%20to%20the%20period%20up%20to%20financial%20year%202009-10%2C%20and%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%20for%20financial%20years%202010-11%20to%202014-15.%20This%20is%20expected%20to%20benefit%20about%20a%20crore%20taxpayers%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20did%20not%20make%20changes%20to%20tax%20slabs%20in%20the%20interim%20Budget%20in%20keeping%20with%20convention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20for%20tax%20proposals%2C%20in%20keeping%20with%20the%20convention%2C%20I%20do%20not%20propose%20to%20make%20any%20changes%20relating%20to%20taxation%20and%20propose%20to%20retain%20the%20same%20tax%20rates%20for%20direct%20taxes%20and%20indirect%20taxes%20including%20import%20duties%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20certain%20tax%20benefits%20to%20start-ups%20and%20investments%20made%20by%20sovereign%20wealth%20or%20pension%20funds%20as%20also%20tax%20exemption%20on%20certain%20income%20of%20some%20IFSC%20units%20are%20expiring%20on%2031.03.2024.%20To%20provide%20continuity%20in%20taxation%2C%20I%20propose%20to%20extend%20the%20date%20to%2031.03.2025%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706770860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-09%2Fcqjbnl_rupee-generic_625x300_20_September_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Finterim-budget-2024-direct-tax-demand-up-to-rs-25-000-to-be-withdrawn-see-key-details-4972136%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Centre%20will%20not%20pursue%20taxpayers%20to%20recover%20old%20direct%20taxes%20up%20to%20Rs%2025%2C000%20till%20the%20financial%20year%202009-10%2C%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20said%20in%20her%20interim%20Budget%202024%20speech%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Finterim-budget-2024-direct-tax-demand-up-to-rs-25-000-to-be-withdrawn-see-key-details-4972136%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Finterim-budget-2024-direct-tax-demand-up-to-rs-25-000-to-be-withdrawn-see-key-details-4972136%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Finterim-budget-2024-direct-tax-demand-up-to-rs-25-000-to-be-withdrawn-see-key-details-4972136%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IIT%20Bombay%20Cancels%20Lecture%20on%20'Crisis%20in%20Indian%20Education'