0Devy%20as%20he%20is%20an%20intellectual%20personality%20who%20delivers%20his%20thoughts%20on%20history%20and%20present%20society.%20We%20were%20very%20happy%20when%20the%20institute%20decided%20to%20invite%20him%20to%20the%20campus.%20But%20going%20by%20past%20instances%2C%20we%20feared%20that%20the%20institute%20may%20cancel%20the%20lecture%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fmumbai-news%2Fiit-bombay-cancels-lecture-by-gn-devy-101706641203094.html%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20student%20from%20the%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fiit-bombay-cancels-conference-left-education-ministry%5C%22%3E%20IIT%20Bombay%20Cancels%20Conference%20on%20Left%20Movement%20After%20%E2%80%98Call%20From%20Senior%20Official%E2%80%99%20in%20Edu%20Ministry%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Devy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fmumbai-news%2Fiit-bombay-cancels-lecture-by-gn-devy-101706641203094.html%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20never%20been%20previously%20associated%20with%20IIT%20Bombay.%20A%20professor%20from%20the%20institute%E2%80%99s%20lecture%20committee%20invited%20me%20to%20give%20a%20lecture.%20But%20a%20day%20before%20I%20was%20leaving%2C%20the%20same%20person%20called%20to%20inform%20me%20about%20cancellation%20of%20the%20lecture.%20I%20did%20not%20even%20bother%20to%20ask%20the%20reason%20as%20it%20is%20not%20my%20basic%20right.%20I%20have%20ample%20of%20pending%20work%2C%20so%20I%20utilised%20the%20time%20for%20the%20same.%E2%80%9D%20However%2C%20he%20added%20that%20%E2%80%9CSuch%20last-minute%20cancellations%20do%20leave%20a%20bitter%20taste.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20difficult%20for%20me%20to%20understand%20the%20motivation%20behind%20calling%20off%20the%20event.%20If%20I%20could%20deliver%20a%20lecture%20at%20IIT-Guwahati%2C%20another%20central%20institute%2C%20governed%20by%20the%20same%20regulations%2C%20then%20why%20not%20IIT-Bombay%3F%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmumbai%2Fdifficult-to-understand-why-iit-b-lecture-was-cancelled%2Farticleshow%2F107307803.cms%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20Devy%20while%20speaking%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20sent%20them%20the%20synopsis%20of%20the%20lecture%20almost%20a%20month%20ago.%20The%20discussion%20over%20this%20started%20about%20four%20to%20five%20months%20ago%20and%20after%20a%20lot%20of%20deliberations%20on%20both%20sides%2C%20Jan%2031%20was%20finalised%20for%20the%20talk.%20The%20book%20that%20I%20was%20going%20to%20speak%20about%20is%20published%20and%20is%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20I%20do%20not%20think%20this%20has%20anything%20to%20do%20with%20the%20content%20of%20the%20book%20or%20the%20topic%20of%20the%20lecture%2C%20nor%20do%20I%20wish%20to%20build%20a%20hypothesis%20around%20it.%20They%20are%20a%20scientific%20organisation%2C%20and%20I%20would%20like%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20reasons%20are%20not%20irrational%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmumbai%2Fdifficult-to-understand-why-iit-b-lecture-was-cancelled%2Farticleshow%2F107307803.cms%5C%22%3Eadded%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20the%20keynote%20speaker%20at%20IIT-Guwahati%E2%80%99s%20Graduate%20Research%20Meet%20in%20October%20last%20year%20and%20spoke%20on%20%E2%80%98Describing%20India%3A%20People%E2%80%99s%20Movements%20and%20Knowledge%20Production%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20the%20first%20lecture%20cancelled%20at%20IIT%20Bombay%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20institute%20had%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fiit-bombay-cancels-conference-left-education-ministry%5C%22%3Ecancelled%20a%20lecture%20titled%20%E2%80%98Israel-Palestine%3A%20The%20Historical%20Context%E2