Supreme%20Court%2C%20freedom%20of%20speech%20cannot%20be%20absolute%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20RWA%20also%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20%E2%80%98IT-cell%E2%80%99%20chief%20Amit%20Malviya%20has%20posted%20on%20X%20saying%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cterse%20letter%E2%80%9D%20should%20%E2%80%9Cserve%20as%20a%20message%20for%20everyone%2C%20who%20think%20abusing%20Hindu%20beliefs%20is%20par%20for%20the%20course.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%20questioned%20the%20legality%20of%20the%20RWA%E2%80%99s%20move%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Cterrifying%E2%80%9D%20example%20of%20%E2%80%9CNew%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20have%20dismissed%20it%20(the%20incident)%20as%20laughable%20were%20it%20not%20be%20tragic%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20to%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20only%20responding%20because%20these%20kind%20of%20incidents%20are%20tragic.%20I%20would%20never%20agree%20with%20you%20on%20a%20hundred%20issues.%20I%20may%20not%20agree%20with%20Mr%20Aiyar%20or%20his%20daughter%20on%20a%20hundred%20issues.%20But%20that%20is%20not%20the%20issue%20at%20all.%20How%20can%20I%20not%20allow%20your%20right%20to%20disagree%20with%20me%3F%20And%20what%20legality%20and%20constitutionality%20is%20there%20to%20ask%20him%20to%20get%20out%20of%20his%20colony%20because%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20like%20what%20he%20says%3F%20This%20is%20terrifying%20in%20new%20India.%20He%20has%20the%20full%20right%20to%20disagree%20but%20can%20one%20neighbour%20tell%20the%20other%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20house%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhome-ministry-cancels-centre-for-policy-researchs-fcra-registration%5C%22%3Ecancelled%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Foreign%20Contribution%20Regulation%20Act%20(FCRA)%20registration%20of%2