n%20of%20balances%20by%20its%20customers%20from%20their%20accounts%20including%20savings%20bank%20accounts%2C%20current%20accounts%2C%20prepaid%20instruments%2C%20FASTags%2C%20National%20Common%20Mobility%20Cards%2C%20etc.%20are%20to%20be%20permitted%20without%20any%20restrictions%2C%20up%20to%20their%20available%20balance%2C%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20RBI%20Has%20Put%20Restrictions%20On%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20said%20it%20had%20in%20March%202022%20asked%20the%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20to%20stop%20adding%20new%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20Comprehensive%20System%20Audit%20report%20and%20subsequent%20compliance%20validation%20report%20of%20the%20external%20auditors%20revealed%20persistent%20non-compliances%20and%20continued%20material%20supervisory%20concerns%20in%20the%20bank%2C%20warranting%20further%20supervisory%20action%2C%20the%20RBI%20said%2C%20without%20disclosing%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20action%20against%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frbi-action-paytm-payments-bank-the-only-services-allowed-are-4967226%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPaytm%20Payments%20Bank%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20taken%20under%20Section%2035A%20of%20the%20Banking%20Regulation%20Act%2C%201949%2C%20the%20central%20bank%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20Said%20On%20RBI%20Restrictions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaytm%20Payments%20Bank%2C%20an%20associate%20of%20One%2097%20Communications%20Limited%20(OCL)%2C%20said%20it%20is%20taking%20%26quot%3Bimmediate%20steps%26quot%3B%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20RBI's%20directions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOCL%2C%20as%20a%20payments%20company%2C%20works%20with%20various%20banks%20(not%20just%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank)%2C%20on%20various%20payments%20products%2C%20the%20fintech%20company%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote