with%20an%20endorsement%20from%20Speaker%20of%20the%20House%20Mike%20Johnson%2C%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Fhouse-vote-tax-bill-child-tax-credit-business%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20in%20a%20Wednesday%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it's%20%26quot%3Bimportant%20bipartisan%20legislation%20to%20revive%20conservative%20pro-growth%20tax%20reform.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20bottom-up%20process%20is%20a%20good%20example%20of%20how%20Congress%20is%20supposed%20to%20make%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20legislation%20%E2%80%94%20a%20rare%20bipartisan%20feat%20%E2%80%94%20would%20both%20boost%20the%20child%20tax%20credit%20and%20offer%20GOP-friendly%20tax%20relief%20for%20businesses%20that%20invest%20in%20research%20and%20development%2C%20among%20other%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20refundable%20child%20tax%20credit%20would%20be%20increased%20from%20%241%2C600%20a%20child%20to%20%241%2C800%20in%202023%20and%20would%20rise%20to%20%242%2C000%20by%202025.%20In%20the%20first%20year%20of%20the%20legislation%20alone%2C%20the%20left-leaning%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbpp.org%2Fresearch%2Ffederal-tax%2Fabout-16-million-children-in-low-income-families-would-gain-in-first-year-of%23about-16-million-children-in-cbpp-anchor%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ECenter%20on%20Budget%20and%20Policy%20Priorities%20estimates%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20would%20lift%20up%20to%20400%2C000%20kids%20out%20of%20poverty%3B%20by%20the%20time%20it's%20fully%20in%20effect%2C%20half%20a%20million%20children%20would%20rise%20above%20the%20poverty%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHouseholds%20set%20to%20benefit%20from%20the%20proposal%20would%20see%20their%202023%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etax%20bills%20cut%20by%20%24680%2C%20according%20to%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.taxpolicycenter.org%2Ftaxvox%2Fbipartisan-ctc-framework-would-help-lowest-income-quintiles%5C%22%20target%3D%5