ning%20and%20executing%20successful%20overnight%20company%20retreats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20benefits%20of%20a%20company%20retreat%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20employees%2C%20the%20new%20setting%20that%20comes%20with%20a%20company%20retreat%20is%20a%20welcome%20change%20and%20can%20boost%20motivation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20overnight%20retreat%20can%20cultivate%20a%20great%20environment%20for%20team-building%2C%20offering%20extended%20time%20for%20collaborative%20activities%20that%20enhance%20communication%20and%20trust%20among%20team%20members%2C%26quot%3B%20Brittany%20Dolin%2C%20a%20cofounder%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pocketbookagency.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Pocketbook%20Agency%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20boutique%20recruiting%20firm%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20change%20of%20scenery%20can%20spark%20creativity%20by%20providing%20employees%20with%20a%20break%20from%20routine%20to%20foster%20fresh%20ideas%20and%20perspectives%2C%20and%20the%20retreat%20becomes%20a%20shared%20experience%2C%20contributing%20to%20a%20more%20positive%20work%20atmosphere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222452%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Brittany%20Dolin%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b9394d7a3d27148875e1f5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223678%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBrittany%20Dolin%2C%20a%20cofounder%20of%20Pocketbook%20Agency.%3Cp%3EAudrey%20Ma%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20employees%20scattered%20across%20the%20state%20or%20country%2C%20a%20company%20retreat%20is%20also%20a%20chance%20to%20bring%20everyone%20together%20and%20reinforce%20a%20positive%20company%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20your%20goals%20include%20fostering%20community%2C%20an%20overnight%20'off-site'%20retreat%20is%20a%20great%20idea%2C%26quot%3B%20Alex%20Barrett%2C%20the%20senior%20director%20of%20strategy%20and%20innovation%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theknowledgehouse.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Knowledge%20House%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20organization%20that%20provides%20digital-skills%20training%20for%20underserved%20communities%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BDuring%20our%20last%20retreat%2C%20we%20welcomed%20all%20of%20our%20C-suite%20staff%20members%20to%20New%20York%20from%20our%20expansion%20cities%3A%20Atlanta%2C%20Newark%2C%20and%20Los%20Angeles.%20Our%20out-of-town%20staff%20members%20got%20to%20experience%20NYC%20for%20three%20days%20after%20attending%20our%20daily%20retreat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221292%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alex%20Barrett%20headshot%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b95029ac2de4f17ee5f833%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221292%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlex%20Barrett%2C%20the%20senior%20director%20of%20strategy%20and%20innovation%20at%20The%20Knowledge%20House.%3Cp%3ECecilia%20Sanchez%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20company%20retreat%20can%20also%20provide%20casual%2C%20low-stakes%20spaces%20for%20senior%20and%20junior-level%20employees%20to%20socialize.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20retreat%20can%20provide%20an%20informal%20setting%20that%20allows%20colleagues%20to%20get%20to%20know%20each%20other%20better%20without%20the%20focus%20being%20on%20deliverables%20or%20meetings%2C%26quot%3B%20Leanne%20Mair%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.benefactumconsulting.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBenefactum%20Consulting%2C%20said.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3BIt%20can%20also%20offer%20powerful%20networking%20and%20career%20opportunities%2C%20and%20employees%20can%20showcase%20their%20thoughts%20and%20ideas%20to%20senior%20staff%20members.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20importance%20of%20including%20employees%20in%20decision-making%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20run%20a%20successful%20retreat%2C%20employees%20need%20to%20be%20on%20board%20early%20and%20feel%20included%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20planned%20a%20retreat%2C%20the%20biggest%20challenge%20I%20faced%20was%20persuading%20people%20that%20the%20retreat%20was%20worth%20traveling%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20Mair%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20to%20outline%20why%20a%20retreat%20would%20deliver%20a%20different%20outcome%20than%20brainstorming%20in%20an%20office.%20It%20was%20also%20important%20to%20define%20why%20their%20participation%20was%20important%20and%20what%20benefits%20it%20presented%20to%20each%20participant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223249%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Leanne%20Mair%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b94723ac2de4f17ee5f23b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222168%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELeanne%20Mair%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Benefactum%20Consulting.%3Cp%3ELeanne%20Mair%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBarrett%20said%20that%20though%20it's%20not%20possible%20to%20please%20everyone%2C%20it's%20important%20that%20employees%20feel%20heard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20event%20planner%20knows%20that%20there%20will%20always%20be%20something%20that%20doesn't%20go%20as%20planned%20or%20a%20detail%20that%20gets%20missed%2C%20and%20that's%20OK%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BPlanning%20a%20retreat%20comes%20with%20trade-offs%20that%20won't%20make%20everyone%20happy%20or%20allow%20for%20everyone%20to%20be%20accommodated.%20It's%20the%20HR%20or%20business%20leader's%20job%20to%20make%20decisions%20that%20will%20serve%20their%20team%20and%20company%20best%2C%20knowing%20that%20sometimes%20that%20means%20there%20are%20people%20you%20will%20disappoint%20in%20the%20process.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20to%20choose%20a%20date%20and%20location%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20experts%20BI%20spoke%20to%20recommended%20limiting%20a%20retreat%20to%20two%20or%20three%20nights%20and%20choosing%20a%20location%20convenient%20for%20most%20employees.%20Depending%20on%20your%20budget%2C%20a%20local%20hotel%20or%20lodge%20within%20driving%20distance%20of%20the%20office%20may%20be%20ideal%20for%20a%20first%20company%20retreat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccessibility%20is%20paramount%2C%20as%20a%20convenient%20location%20ensures%20the%20entire%20team%20can%20easily%20travel%20to%20the%20destination%2C%26quot%3B%20Nicole%20Dayan%2C%20a%20cofounder%20of%20the%20recruiting%20firm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pocketbookagency.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Pocketbook%20Agency%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BBudget%20considerations%20will%20also%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20deciding%20your%20location%2C%20and%20you'll%20need%20to%20do%20a%20realistic%20assessment%20of%20all%20costs%20related%20to%20travel%2C%20accommodation%2C%20meals%2C%20and%20planned%20activities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20important%20to%20consider%20the%20time%20of%20year%20for%20a%20company%20retreat.%20A%20slow%20time%20at%20the%20office%20doesn't%20always%20coincide%20with%20getting%20the%20best%20travel%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221866%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nicole%20Dayan%20photo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b94fa243bb77284ba1d7cb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENicole%20Dayan%2C%20a%20cofounder%20of%20The%20Pocketbook%20Agency.%3Cp%3EAudrey%20Ma%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20aligning%20the%20retreat%20with%20the%20slow%20business%20season%20can%20help%20mitigate%20operational%20disruptions%2C%20you%20should%20also%20consider%20employee%20preferences%20and%20budget%20constraints%2C%26quot%3B%20Dayan%20said.%20%26quot%3BWeather%20conditions%20must%20be%20taken%20into%20account%2C%20particularly%20if%20outdoor%20activities%20are%20on%20the%20agenda.%20Scheduling%20the%20retreat%20during%20favorable%20weather%20ensures%20an%20enjoyable%20atmosphere%2C%20particularly%20for