tivities%20is%20counterproductive%20to%20creating%20an%20atmosphere%20where%20everyone%20feels%20engaged%20and%20motivated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20knowledge%20house%20retreat%20class%20photo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b9510eac2de4f17ee5f8a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223376%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Knowledge%20House's%202023%20retreat%20class%20photo.%3Cp%3EThe%20Knowledge%20House%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20so%20many%20moving%20parts%2C%20it's%20also%20wise%20to%20consider%20hiring%20a%20third-party%20company%20to%20plan%20a%20retreat%20or%20to%20coordinate%20the%20retreat%20activities%2C%20Dolin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConsider%20leveraging%20the%20expertise%20of%20facilitators%20or%20event%20planners%20if%20you%20have%20a%20large%20staff%20or%20employees%20traveling%20from%20different%20cities%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BMany%20event-planning%20companies%20offer%20services%20tailored%20to%20corporate%20retreats%20and%20can%20help%20with%20various%20aspects%20of%20the%20retreat%2C%20including%20venue%20selection%2C%20itinerary%20planning%2C%20team-building%20activities%2C%20catering%2C%20and%20logistics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarrett%20said%20to%20consider%20sending%20out%20a%20survey%20after%20the%20retreat%20and%20using%20that%20feedback%20to%20plan%20the%20next%20retreat.%20Ultimately%2C%20your%20employees%20will%20feel%20they%20spent%20their%20time%20well%20if%20the%20experience%20lines%20up%20with%20the%20outlined%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20hosting%20an%20intentional%20retreat%2C%20being%20able%20to%20clearly%20articulate%20why%20a%20company%20is%20choosing%20to%20gather%20and%20have%20leaders%20align%20what%20they%20hope%20to%20accomplish%20together%20is%20the%20key%20ingredient%20for%20success%2C%26quot%3B%20Barrett%20said.%20%26quot%3BReme