E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Soren's%20petition%20will%20be%20heard%20by%20the%20bench%20of%20Acting%20Chief%20Justice%20Shree%20Chandrashekhar%20and%20Justice%20Anubha%20Rawat%20Choudhary%20at%2010.30%20am%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706728800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F6b1u0oqg_hemant-soren-ani_625x300_01_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhemant-soren-approaches-jharkhand-high-court-petition-to-be-heard-today-4969553%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Chief%20Minister%20Hemant%20Soren%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%2C%20moved%20the%20Jharkhand%20High%20Court%20on%20Wednesday%20night.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhemant-soren-approaches-jharkhand-high-court-petition-to-be-heard-today-4969553%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhemant-soren-approaches-jharkhand-high-court-petition-to-be-heard-today-4969553%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhemant-soren-approaches-jharkhand-high-court-petition-to-be-heard-today-4969553%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bombay%20High%20Court%20Passes%20Split%20Verdict%20On%20Petition%20Challenging%20Fact-Checking%20Unit%20Rules%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F28022009%2FBombay-high-court-lit-up-at-night.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Bombay%20high%20court%20on%20Wednesday%20(January%2031)%20delivered%20a%20split%20verdict%20on%20the%20petition%20seeking%20to%20strike%20down%20rules%203(i)(II)(A)%20and%20(C)%20of%20the%20IT%20Amendment%20Rules%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20rules%20give%20the%20Union%20government%20powers%20to%20set%20up%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfact-checking%20unit%E2%80%9D%20(FCU)%20to%20assess%20social%20media%20posts%20and%20term%20posts%20as%20%E2%80%9Cfake%2C%20false%20or%20misleading%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20was%20filed%20by%20stand-up%20comedian%20and%20political%20satirist%20Kunal%20Kamra%2C%20the%20Association%20of%20Indian%20Magazines%2C%20the%20News%20Broadcasters%20and%20Digital%20Association%20and%20the%20Editors%E2%80%99%20Guild%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20division%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Gautam%20Patel%20and%20Neela%20Gokhale%20presided%20over%20the%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Justice%20Patel%20passed%20an%20order%20favouring%20the%20petitioners%2C%20Justice%20Gokhale%20upheld%20the%20amendment%20made%20to%20the%20Rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20will%20now%20be%20referred%20to%20another%20judge%20and%20meanwhile%2C%20the%20FCU%20will%20not%20be%20notified%20for%20the%20coming%20ten%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20amended%20rules%2C%20once%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20FCU%20identifies%20content%20as%20fake%2C%20false%20or%20misleading%2C%20social%20media%20platforms%20like%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20Instagram%20and%20Facebook%20would%20either%20have%20to%20take%20the%20content%20down%20content%20or%20add%20a%20disclaimer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Patel%2C%20in%20a%20148-page%20order%2C%20however%2C%20observed%20that%20the%20state%20classifying%20speech%20as%20%E2%80%9Ctrue%20or%20false%E2%80%9D%20and%20compelling%20its%20non-publication%20could%20be%20%E2%80%9Cnothing%20but%20censorship%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20Navroz%20Seervai%2C%20appearing%20for%20Kamra%2C%20had%20raised%20concerns%20over%20the%20lack%20of%20remedies%20available%20to%20social%20media%20platform%20users%20in%20the%20event%20of%20their%20content%20being%20flagged%20as%20fake%2C%20false%20or%20misleading.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeervai%20had%20also%20argued%20that%20the%20said%20IT%20rule%20violates%20the%20principles%20of%20natural%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20battery%20of%20seasoned%20lawyers%2C%20including%20senior%20advocates%20Darius%20Khambata%20and%20Arvind%20Datar%20and%20advocates%20Shadan%20Farasat%20and%20Gautam%20Bhatia%2C%20appeared%20for%20the%20petitioners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20had%20pointed%20out%20that%20allowing%20the%20government%20to%20decide%20what%20is%20fake%20and%20false%20risks%20arbitrary%20and%20discriminative%20orders%20and%20would%20directly%20violate%20Articles%2014%20and%2019%20(1)(A)%20of%20the%20constitution%20along%20with%20the%20principles%20of%20natural%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDatar%20had%20argued%20that%20the%20rule%20attempts%20to%20exceed%20the%20restrictions%20imposed%20on%20the%20right%20to%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%20under%20Article%2019(2)%20of%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%2019(2)%20permits%20the%20government%20to%20impose%20%E2%80%9Creasonable%20restrictions%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%20%E2%80%9Cin%20the%20interests%20of%20public%20order%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolicitor%20general%20Tushar%20Mehta%2C%20appearing%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20had%20spoken%20of%20the%20dangers%20of%20allowing%20fake%20news%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%2C%20Justice%20Patel%20observed%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6in%20our%20constitutional%20scheme%2C%20free%20speech%20is%20always%20to%20be%20under-regulated%2C%20and%20the%20restrictions%20on%20it%20%E2%80%93%20attempts%20at%20control%20and%20abridgement%20%E2%80%93%20must%20be%20over-regulated%2C%20not%20the%20other%20way%20around.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20a%20finding%20that%20there%20is%20a%20fundamental%20right%20to%20falsehood%20or%20fake%20news%20or%20deepfakes.%20Quite%20the%20contrary.%20That%20is%20not%20even%20the%20question%20before%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20issue%20is%20whether%20the%20state%20has%2C%20in%20our%20constitutional%20set-up%2C%20an%20overriding%20authority%20to%20arrive%20at%20an%20absolutist%20determination%20of%20both%20content%20and%20expression%20as%20%E2%80%98the%20truth%E2%80%99%20and%20to%20compel%20a%20particular%20form%20of%20content%20and%20expression%3F%20I%20would%20have%20the%20greatest%20difficulty%20in%20accepting%20a%20proposition%20of%20this%20width.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20support%20his%20argument%2C%20Mehta%20had%20played%20video%20clips%20showing%20deepfakes%20of%20Hollywood%20actor%20Morgan%20Freeman%20and%20other%20well-known%20personalities%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Gokhale%2C%20in%20her%2092-page%20order%20upholding%20the%20amended%20FCU%20clause%2C%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CNot%20only%20can%20belief%20in%20misinformation%20lead%20to%20poor%20judgments%20and%20decision%20making%2C%20but%20it%20also%20exerts%20a%20lingering%20influence%20on%20people%E2%80%99s%20reasoning%20even%20after%20it%20has%20been%20corrected.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20further%20observed%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdangers%20of%20fake%20news%20on%20social%20media%20intermediaries%20cannot%20be%20played%20down%20any%20longer%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20in%20this%20scenario%20that%20the%20government%20appears%20to%20have%20framed%20the%20impugned%20rule%20to%20curb%20the%20menace%20of%20fake%2C%20false%2C%20and%20misleading%20information%20related%20to%20business%20of%20the%20government.%20On%20an%20exacting%20understanding%20of%20the%20rule%2C%20the%20information%20to%20be%20offensive%20must%20be%20shared%20with%20the%20knowledge%20that%20it%20is%20not%20genuine%20and%20is%20shared%20with%20malicious%20intent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20order%2C%20Justice%20Gokhale%20acknowledged%20that%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvibrant%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9Clargest%20democracy%20in%20the%20world%E2%80%9D%2C%20there%20is%20bound%20to%20be%20a%20%E2%80%9Csuspicion%E2%80%9D%20regarding%20the%20intent%20of%20the%20government%20in%20introducing%20a%20provision%20such%20as%20the%20FCU%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20apprehensions%20of%20the%20petitioners%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Care%20also%20justified%20and%20cannot%20be%20swept%20away%20as%20frivolous%20or%20motivated.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20regulating%20free%20speech%20to%20the%20limited%20extent%20of%20fake%2C%20false%20and%20misleading%20information%20in%20a%20way%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20create%20better%20conditions%20for%20citizens%20to%20sift%20facts%20from%20fake%20and%20make%20informed%20decisions%20about%20what%20and%20how%20they%20want%20their%20societies%20to%20be%2C%20based%20on%20an%20opportunity%20to%20receive%20unadulterated%20information.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Justice%20Gokhale%2C%20the%20rule%20%E2%80%9Cmeets%20the%20test%20of%20proportionality%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%5BThe%5D%20right%20of%20citizens%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20representative%20and%20participative%20democracy%20of%20the%20county%20is%20meaningless%20unless%20they%20have%20access%20to%20authentic%20information%20and%20are%20not%20misled%20by%20misinformation%2C%20information%20which%20is%20patently%20untrue%2C%20fake%2C%20false%2C%20or%20misleading%2C%20knowingly%20communicated%20with%20malicious%20intent%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20wrote%20in%20her%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGokhale%20also%20said%20that%20the%20measures%20adopted%20by%20the%20government%20are%20%E2%80%9Cconsistent%20with%20the%20object%20of%20the%20law%20and%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20encroachment%20on%20a%20fundamental%20right%20is%20not%20disproportionate%20to%20the%20benefit%20which%20is%20likely%20to%20ensue%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatel%2C%20however%2C%20observed%20that%20%E2%80%9Cit%20is%20unthinkable%20that%20any%20one%20entity%20%E2%80%93%20be%20it%20the%20government%20or%20anyone%20else%20%E2%80%93%20can%20unilaterally%20%E2%80%98identified%E2%80%99%2C%20(meaning%20picked%20out%20and%20decided)%20to%20be%20fake%2C%20false%20or%20misleading.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20surely%20cannot%20be%20the%20sole%20preserve%20of%20the%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20observed%20as%20he%20went%20on%20to%20express%20his%20regret%20for%20not%20being%20able%20to%20persuade%20Justice%20Gokhale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20regret%20that%20I%20have%20been%20unable%20to%20persuade%20Justice%20Gokhale%20to%20my%20perspective%2C%20nor%20I%20to%20share%20hers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%20in%20his%20concluding%20remark%20in%20the%20judgement.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706726384000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F28022009%2FBombay-high-court-lit-up-at-night.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbombay-hc-split-verdict-petition-it-amendment-rules%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20matter%20will%20now%20be%20referred%20to%20another%20judge%20and%20meanwhile%2C%20the%20government's%20fact-checking%20unit%20will%20not%20be%20notified%20for%20the%20next%20ten%20days.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbombay-hc-split-verdict-petition-it-amendment-rules%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Day%20Before%20Retiring%2C%20Varanasi%20Judge%20Hands%20Over%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20Basement%20to%20Hindus%20For%20Worship%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F23142008%2FGyan-vapi-mosque-min.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20district%20judge%20in%20Varanasi%20on%20Wednesday%20(January%2031)%20%E2%80%93%20his%20last%20working%20day%20before%20retirement%20%E2%80%93%20allowed%20Hindus%20to%20worship%20inside%20a%20sealed%20basement%20of%20the%20the%20Mughal-era%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20in%20a%20decision%20that%20could%20have%20far-reaching%20consequences%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid-Kashi%20Vishwanath%20Temple%20legal%20matter%20that%20is%20being%20heard%20in%20courts%20at%20all%20three%20levels%20of%20the%20judiciary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Hindu%20priests%20and%20Hindu%20devotees%20visiting%20the%20Kashi%20Vishwanath%20Temple%20would%20also%20get%20access%20to%20visit%20and%20perform%20%3Cem%3Epuja%3C%2Fem%3E%20inside%20the%20%3Cem%3Etehkhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindu%20plaintiffs%2C%20who%20are%20seeking%20religious%20rights%20within%20the%20mosque%20as%20well%20as%20its%20ultimate%20possession%20from%20Muslims%2C%20dubbed%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20order%20as%20a%20victory%20and%20equated%20it%20to%20the%20controversial%20unlocking%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20in%201986.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Babri%20Masjid%20was%20eventually%20demolished%20by%20a%20mob%20of%20Hindu%20activists%20assembled%20at%20the%20call%20of%20members%20of%20the%20Sangh%20%3Cem%3Eparivar%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20December%206%2C%201992.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20caretakers%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20were%20stunned%20by%20the%20district%20court%20order%20and%20said%20the%20court%20accepted%20claims%20made%20by%20the%20temple%20side%20without%20seeking%20any%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Varanasi%20court%20order%20comes%20days%20after%20the%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%20(ASI)%20in%20its%20survey%20report%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fasis-survey-report-says-a-large-hindu-temple-existed-under-the-gyanvapi-mosque%5C%22%3Eclaimed%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Clarge%20Hindu%20temple%E2%80%9D%20existed%20there%3C%2Fa%3E%20prior%20to%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20existing%20structure%20%E2%80%93%20i.e.%2C%20the%20mosque%20%E2%80%93%20and%20that%20parts%20of%20the%20temple%20were%20modified%20and%20used%20in%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Islamic%20place%20of%20worship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDistrict%20judge%20Ajaya%20Krishna%20Vishvesha%20directed%20the%20district%20administration%20to%20make%20arrangements%20for%20puja%20and%20other%20Hindu%20activities%20inside%20the%20southern%20tehkhana%2C%20or%20cellar%2C%20of%20the%20mosque%20within%20seven%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudge%20Vishvesha%20directed%20the%20administration%20to%20conduct%20the%20puja%20and%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Erag-bhog%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cidols%E2%80%9D%20inside%20the%20tehkhana%20through%20a%20priest%20appointed%20by%20the%20Shri%20Kashi%20Vishwanath%20Temple%20Trust%2C%20which%20manages%20the%20adjoining%20Kashi%20Vishwanath%20Mandir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20passed%20the%20order%20on%20an%20application%20filed%20by%20local%20priest%20Shailendra%20Kumar%20Pathak%20of%20the%20Acharya%20Ved%20Vyas%20Peeth%20temple%2C%20who%20had%20sought%20rights%20to%20worship%20the%20Maa%20Shringar%20Gauri%20and%20other%20alleged%20visible%20and%20invisible%20deities%20he%20claimed%20were%20in%20the%20cellar%20of%20the%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20caretakers%20of%20the%20mosque%20rejected%20all%20claims%20made%20by%20Pathak%20that%20there%20were%20idols%20kept%20inside%20the%20previously%20sealed%20cellar%20and%20that%20his%20ancestors%20used%20to%20carry%20out%20puja%20inside%20the%20cellar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudge%20Vishvesha%2C%20however%2C%20ruled%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Hindu%20plaintiff%20and%20directed%20the%20district%20administration%20to%20make%20the%20necessary%20iron%20fencing%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20puja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20district%20magistrate%20had%20on%20January%2024%20completed%20the%20process%20of%20taking%20over%20the%20cellar%20after%20the%20court%20on%20January%2017%20directed%20the%20district%20magistrate%20to%20keep%20the%20cellar%20secure%20and%20appointed%20him%20as%20its%20receiver.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20application%2C%20Pathak%20claimed%20that%20there%20were%20idols%20kept%20in%20the%20southern%20cellar%20of%20the%20mosque%20and%20that%20his%20ancestors%20as%20priests%20conducted%20worship%20of%20the%20idols%20kept%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Pathak%20further%20claimed%20that%20%E2%80%9CPujari%20Vyas%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20or%20Somnath%20Vyas%2C%20his%20maternal%20grandfather%2C%20was%20prevented%20from%20entering%20the%20barricaded%20area%20of%20the%20mosque%20after%20December%201993.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rag-bhog%20and%20%3Cem%3Esanskar%3C%2Fem%3E%20rituals%20were%20also%20stopped%2C%20Pathak%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20ancient%20Hindu%20idols%20and%20several%20other%20religious%20items%20linked%20to%20the%20Hindu%20religion%20were%20inside%20the%20cellar.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20necessary%20to%20carry%20out%20regular%20puja%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Emurtis%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5Bidols%5D%20inside%20the%20tehkhana%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20management%20committee%20of%20the%20Anjuman%20Intezamia%20Masajid%2C%20which%20manages%20the%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%2C%20vehemently%20denied%20the%20claims%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20in%20written%20applications%20told%20the%20court%20that%20no%20member%20of%20the%20Vyas%20family%20ever%20carried%20out%20puja%20in%20the%20cellar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20the%20question%20of%20stopping%20someone%20from%20conducting%20puja%20from%20December%201993%20does%20not%20arise%2C%20the%20committee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20alleged%20idol%20was%20ever%20present%20at%20the%20site%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20committee%20said%20and%20denied%20Pathak%E2%80%99s%20claims%20that%20his%20family%20had%20ancestral%20occupation%20of%20the%20cellar.%20The%20cellar%20has%20always%20been%20under%20the%20occupation%20of%20the%20mosque%20committee%2C%20the%20caretakers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishnu%20Shankar%20Jain%2C%20one%20of%20the%20lawyers%20for%20the%20temple%20side%20in%20the%20matter%2C%20hailed%20the%20court%20order%20as%20historic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDistrict%20court%20Varanasi%20has%20created%20history%20today%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jain%20tweeted%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20reporters%2C%20he%20said%20this%20was%20the%20first%20step%20for%20Hindus%20towards%20gaining%20ownership%20of%20the%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJustice%20K.M%20Pandey%20during%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20movement%20ordered%20the%20opening%20of%20the%20locks%20%5Bof%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%5D%20on%20February%201%2C%201986.%20I%20see%20this%20order%20in%20a%20similar%20vein.%20This%20is%20the%20turning%20point%20in%20this%20case.%20It%20is%20a%20historic%20order%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jain%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES.M.%20Yasin%2C%20joint%20secretary%20of%20the%20masjid%20committee%2C%20was%20dismayed%20by%20the%20court%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20we%20have%20no%20hope%20of%20justice%20in%20this%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yasin%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYasin%20rejected%20the%20claims%20made%20by%20the%20temple%20side%20and%20said%20that%20no%20puja%20had%20ever%20been%20held%20in%20the%20tehkhana%20and%20that%20there%20are%20no%20idols%20there.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20only%20bamboo%20poles%20there.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20are%20all%20lies.%20They%20have%20no%20evidence.%20The%20court%20passed%20the%20order%20without%20any%20evidence%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yasin%20continued%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20questioned%20why%20the%20judge%20did%20not%20seek%20a%20factual%20position%20from%20the%20district%20administration%2C%20which%20had%20sealed%20the%20cellar%20and%20barricaded%20the%20premises%20in%201995%20on%20the%20directions%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20cellar%20has%20always%20been%20in%20our%20possession%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Yasin%2C%20who%20objected%20to%20the%20breach%20of%20the%20old%20barricade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyers%20of%20the%20mosque%20side%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Deen%20Mohammad%20suit%20of%201937%20did%20not%20make%20any%20mention%20of%20a%20Vyas%20family%20occupying%20the%20tehkhana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Giriraj%20Singh%2C%20commenting%20on%20the%20development%2C%20said%20that%20just%20two%20cellars%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20had%20been%20opened%20and%20the%20others%20were%20still%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%20too%2C%20Hindus%20offered%20puja%20there.%20But%20it%20was%20later%20prevented.%20The%20court%20has%20not%20given%20something%20new%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20posted%20on%20X%3A%20%E2%80%9CDue%20process%20has%20to%20be%20maintained%20while%20following%20any%20court%20order.%20The%20Varanasi%20Court%20fixed%20a%207%20day%20period%20for%20it.%20What%20we%20are%20seeing%20now%20is%20a%20concerted%20effort%20to%20go%20beyond%20the%20due%20process%20and%20prevent%20any%20legal%20recourse%20that%20can%20be%20taken.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20hearing%20is%20on%20February%208%2C%20by%20when%20the%20mosque%20side%20can%20file%20their%20objections.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706722745000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F23142008%2FGyan-vapi-mosque-min.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fjudge-hands-over-gyanvapi-basement-to-hindus%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20court%20passed%20the%20order%20on%20an%20application%20filed%20by%20local%20priest%20who%20sought%20rights%20to%20worship%20the%20Maa%20Shringar%20Gauri%20and%20other%20alleged%20visible%20and%20invisible%20deities%20he%20claimed%20were%20in%20the%20mosque's%20cellar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A48%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fjudge-hands-over-gyanvapi-basement-to-hindus