be%20assisted%20with%20the%20material%20necessary%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324772%2Fbuilding-playgrounds-for-children-india-play-based-learning-education-anthill-creations-infrastructure%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtinue%20their%20education%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Thus%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20the%20school%20kit%20was%20born.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20its%20inception%2C%20Sainwar%20traces%20his%20steps%20back%20to%20an%20article%20he%20read%20in%202014%20about%20a%20Class%2010%20student%20committing%20suicide.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20article%20stated%20that%20the%20child%E2%80%99s%20father%20could%20not%20afford%20a%20bus%20pass%20that%20would%20allow%20him%20to%20travel%20from%20the%20village%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Etaluka%3C%2Fem%3E.%20This%20made%20the%20child%20take%20the%20drastic%20step.%E2%80%9D%20This%20spotlighted%20the%20hardships%20that%20children%20of%20daily%20wage%20workers%20face%2C%20and%20Sainwar%20and%20his%20team%20decided%20to%20investigate%20the%20issue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FIMG-20240124-WA0008-1706162819.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Shivprabha%20Charitable%20Trust%20oversees%20many%20arms%20of%20rural%20development%20including%20education%2C%20health%20services%20and%20entrepreneurship%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FIMG-20240124-WA0008-1706162819.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FIMG-20240124-WA0008-1706162819-300x135.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FIMG-20240124-WA0008-1706162819-500x225.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2