s%20named%20SWAT.%20Today%2C%20he%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20successful%20actors%20in%20China.%20His%20journey%20is%20so%20well%20known%20among%20the%20Chinese%20that%20his%20life%20story%20has%20been%20included%20in%20school%20textbooks%20as%20a%20rags-to-riches%20tale%20of%20inspiration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETina%2C%20a%20teacher%20at%20Xi%E2%80%99an%20International%20Studies%20University%20(XISU)%2C%20China%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CDev%E2%80%99s%20story%20has%20a%20very%20important%20impact%20on%20our%20students.%20It%20took%20a%20lot%20of%20hard%20work%20and%20perseverance%20for%20him%20to%20open%20a%20restaurant%2C%20make%20a%20film%20in%20China%20as%20a%20foreigner%2C%20and%20succeed.%20His%20success%20story%20inspires%20young%20children%20to%20have%20the%20courage%20to%20pursue%20their%20dreams%2C%20defy%20difficulties%20and%20keep%20working%20hard.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDev-Raturi-4-1705931014.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dev%E2%80%99s%20inspiration%20journey%20is%20taught%20in%20the%20schools%20of%20China%20today.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDev-Raturi-4-1705931014.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDev-Raturi-4-1705931014-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDev-Raturi-4-1705931014-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDev-Raturi-4-1705931014-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDev-Raturi-4-1705931014-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338749%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDev%E2%80%99s%20inspirational%20journey%20is%20taught%20in%20the%20schools%20of%20China%20today.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDev%20also%20demonstrated%20the%20importance%20of%20cross-cultural%20communication.%20He%20not%20only%20brought%20Indian%20food%20culture%20to%20China%20but%20also%20spread%20Chinese%20culture%20to%20India%20through%20films%20and%20other%20means.%20This%20kind%20of%20cross-cultural%20exchange%20helps%20to%20improve%20the%20understanding%20and%20friendship%20between%20different%20nationalities%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20an%20Indian%2C%20Dev%20did%20not%20forget%20his%20roots%20after%20tasting%20success%20in%20China.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20he%20has%20brought%20Indian%20culture%20to%20China%20so%20that%20more%20people%20can%20understand%20and%20recognise%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20I%20employ%20nearly%20100%20people%20including%20Chinese%20and%20Indian%20workers.%20And%2030%20percent%20of%20the%20money%20I%20make%20goes%20to%20charity%2C%20either%20in%20India%20or%20China%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Dev.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20an%20honour%20for%20me%20that%20my%20life%20journey%20is%20being%20taught%20in%20Class%207%20in%20schools%20of%20Xi%E2%80%99an%2C%20where%20I%20started%20my%20entrepreneurship%20journey.%20Although%20I%E2%80%99m%20neither%20a%20graduate%20in%20hotel%20management%20nor%20a%20trained%20actor%2C%20I%20visit%20several%20universities%20in%20China%20to%20teach%20students.%20And%20at%20least%2020%20documentaries%20have%20been%20made%20on%20my%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20believe%20if%20you%20are%20passionate%20about%20something%2C%20do%20not%20let%20that%20passion%20die.%20And%20this%20mantra%20helped%20me%20reach%20greater%20heights%20that%20I%20could%20have%20never%20imagined%20coming%20from%20a%20small%20hill%20village%20of%20Uttarakhand%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdit